CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 26 reads: "Thousands Thrilled at Courier Home Service Fair...13. Harry Waugh, Eastern Seaboard representative of Calvert Distillers, was the genial host in their exquisite booth...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Harry Waugh standing at Calvert whiskey booth in the Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
